{"tid":2355510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葛珮帆無理指控「612人道支援基金」支援港獨 李家超拒評：要打擊眾籌作不法用途","createTime":"2021-01-06T06:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T07:41:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd657873714b22364dc54d9b566d3aebf3b9b4d","tid":2355510,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"支援修例風波被補人士的「612人道支援基金」（下稱「基金」）遭建制派狙擊。多名建制派議員聯手在立法會要求政府立法規管網上眾籌，民建聯葛珮帆甚至無證據下指控「基金」是籌款支援港獨行為的組織，保安局局長李家超拒評「基金」情況，又指現時有足夠法律打擊籌集資金作非法行動，包括洗黑錢罪、欺詐罪及《國安法》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210106/VAOTBSKTVRAK7H2YQ562MNYGPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210106%2FVAOTBSKTVRAK7H2YQ562MNYGPQ%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=94c86f40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210106%2FVAOTBSKTVRAK7H2YQ562MNYGPQ%2F&h=6f3a3b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210106/VAOTBSKTVRAK7H2YQ562MNYGPQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f34ccf77c0305dd4f0d9a7b52b36a95cc1cf4560","tid":2355510,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"04358d10ac56646bad24bfa5c5aef5c1328a5b7e","tid":2355510,"uid":268519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"又鳩噏 真係冇腦假博士"},{"pid":"043011b2a76551fa6997af23810784d126db881a","tid":2355510,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"班撚西仲有用處咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e32e2ba758e2e7109476e9beda2b4010e90af5","tid":2355510,"uid":301912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"都估到，佢哋做得一次自然就會有第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0727fe6e4d8872092c52250a038fc3b0883adc42","tid":2355510,"uid":2054,"like":2,